OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775688724
OL,3,CNetanyahu cautiously supports Iran
OL,4,Cceasefire as criticisms within Israel
OL,5,Cgrow
OL,7,FAccording to Benjamin Netanyahu,
OL,8,F"Israel supports President Trump's
OL,9,Fdecision to suspend strikes against
OL,10,FIran for two weeks".
OL,12,FBut not even Israel's prime minister
OL,13,Fis pretending he was party to that
OL,14,Fdecision or that he played a role in
OL,15,Fthe negotiations leading to it.
OL,17,FNetanyahu has tried to portray Israel
OL,18,Fas an equal partner in this war, and
OL,19,Fthere is no doubt that many of the
OL,20,Fmost important air strikes in Iran
OL,21,Fhave been carried out by Israeli jets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
