PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775688724
OL,3,CNetanyahu cautiously supports Iran
OL,4,Cceasefire as criticisms within Israel
OL,5,Cgrow
OL,7,FBut as things dragged on, Israel's and
OL,8,FAmerica's interests have diverged.
OL,10,FThe former is a regional power that
OL,11,Fwas largely unaffected by the blockade
OL,12,Fof the Strait of Hormuz; the United
OL,13,FStates is a superpower with global
OL,14,Fresponsibilities.
OL,16,FThat meant Israel did not share
OL,17,FAmerica's desire to bring hostilities
OL,18,Fto an end.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
