PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775688724
OL,3,CNetanyahu cautiously supports Iran
OL,4,Cceasefire as criticisms within Israel
OL,5,Cgrow
OL,7,FUnlike most Americans, most Israelis
OL,8,Fhave supported the war despite having
OL,9,Fto run into bomb shelters multiple
OL,10,Ftimes, day and night.
OL,12,FIsraelis believe that the more Iran
OL,13,Fwas hammered from the air, the longer
OL,14,Fit would take for the Iranian regime
OL,15,Fto pose a serious threat to Israel
OL,16,Fagain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
