PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775688724
OL,3,CNetanyahu cautiously supports Iran
OL,4,Cceasefire as criticisms within Israel
OL,5,Cgrow
OL,7,FToday, Netanyahu's critics are
OL,8,Fclaiming that the pause has come
OL,9,Fwithout any of Israel's strategic
OL,10,Fobjectives being achieved - the
OL,11,Fnuclear programme has not been totally
OL,12,Fdestroyed; the ballistic missile
OL,13,Fthreat remains and the regime has
OL,14,Fsurvived.
OL,16,FWhile Israel did not have a say when
OL,17,Fit comes to the Iran ceasefire, it
OL,18,Fdoes believe it has a say in Lebanon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
