OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775688724
OL,3,CNetanyahu cautiously supports Iran
OL,4,Cceasefire as criticisms within Israel
OL,5,Cgrow
OL,7,FAnd while reports suggest Hezbollah is
OL,8,Fnow holding fire, the IDF continues to
OL,9,Fmount attacks.
OL,11,FNetanyahu says the two-week ceasefire
OL,12,Fdoes not extend to Lebanon.
OL,14,FIsrael last reached a ceasefire with
OL,15,FHezbollah in November 2024. Then, on
OL,16,FMarch 2, the Iranian proxy opened
OL,17,Ffire, re-igniting that war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
